",["$r","p",null,{"children":["But imagine you later add another dependency to this Effect that needs to re-establish the connection. If this Effect re-synchronizes, it will also call ",["$r","code",null,{"children":"logVisit(roomId)"}]," for the same room, which you did not intend. Logging the visit ",["$r","strong",null,{"children":"is a separate process"}]," from connecting. Write them as two separate Effects:"]}],"
